# Kendall Pond Lodge — Airbnb calendar export (iCal) URL.
# Get it from the Airbnb host dashboard: Calendar -> Availability ->
# Connect/sync calendars -> Export calendar -> copy the iCal link.
# The link contains a private token — keep it local, never commit it.
AIRBNB_KPL_ICAL_URL=

# Optional: sync a local .ics file instead of the live URL.
# KPL_ICAL_FILE=

# Optional: override the data output directory (defaults to data/kpl).
# KPL_DATA_DIR=

# Optional: pin the "as-of" date for testing/demos (YYYY-MM-DD).
# KPL_NOW=
